      "seoTitle": "Evil Dead Review (2013) | WretVision",
      "seoDescription": "A genuinely nasty remake that earns its gore, even if it marks the start of a franchise pattern that's getting old fast.",
      "category": "movie",
      "title": "Evil Dead",
      "year": 2013,
