      "seoTitle": "V/H/S/Beyond Review (2024) | WretVision",
      "seoDescription": "V/H/S/Beyond takes the anthology into orbit and somehow makes that feel smaller than staying on the ground.",
      "category": "movie",
      "title": "V/H/S/Beyond",
      "year": 2024,
      "director": "Jordan Downey",
      "runtime": "114 min",
